#: resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/form/layout.phtml:46
msgid ""
"Whether the married name (from a \"MARRIED\" or \"_MARNM\" name entry) is "
"shown — replacing the birth name, appended in brackets after the birth name, "
"or hidden."
msgstr ""
"是否显示婚后姓名（来自 \"MARRIED\" 或 \"_MARNM\" 类型的姓名条目）— 替换出生姓"
"名、附加在出生姓名后的括号内或隐藏。"

#: resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/form/layout.phtml:53
msgid "Open individual in new browser window/tab"
msgstr "在新的浏览器窗口/标签页中打开个人页面"

#: resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/form/layout.phtml:59
msgid ""
"Open the current individual's detail page in a new browser window/tab when "
"it's left-clicked, otherwise the current window/tab is used."
msgstr "左键点击时在新浏览器窗口/标签页中打开当前个人的详情页面，否则使用当前窗口/标签页。"

#: resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/form/layout.phtml:67
msgid "Show alternative name of individual"
msgstr "显示个人的替代姓名"

#: resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/form/layout.phtml:73
msgid ""
"Displays a person's alternate name, if available. This simultaneously "
"enlarges the individuals' respective boxes to create the necessary space for "
"the display."
msgstr "如有可用，显示个人的替代姓名。这将同时扩大人物的相应框以创建显示所需的空间。"

#: resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/form/orientation.phtml:22
msgid "Orientation"
msgstr "方向"

#: resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/page.phtml:39
msgid "Individual"
msgstr "个人"

#: resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/page.phtml:64
msgid "view"
msgstr "查看"

#: resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/page.phtml:75
msgid "Show more options"
msgstr "显示更多选项"

#: resources/views/modules/descendants-chart/page.phtml:76
msgid "Hide more options"
msgstr "隐藏更多选项"

msgid "Name abbreviation when space is tight"
msgstr "空间不足时的姓名缩写方式"

msgid "Automatic (based on tree's surname tradition)"
msgstr "自动（根据族谱的姓氏传统）"

msgid "Abbreviate given names first"
msgstr "优先缩写名字"

msgid "Abbreviate surnames first"
msgstr "优先缩写姓氏"

msgid "Controls which name part shrinks first when a box is too narrow for the full name. \"Automatic\" uses the tree's surname tradition (Icelandic abbreviates surnames; everything else abbreviates given names)."
msgstr "控制当方框对完整姓名而言过窄时，先缩写哪个名字部分。“自动”使用族谱的姓氏传统（冰岛语缩写姓氏；其他所有传统缩写名字）。"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/display.phtml
msgid "Show nicknames in display names"
msgstr "在显示名中显示昵称"

#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/form/display.phtml
msgid "Inserts the GEDCOM NICK value in quotes between the given names and the surname (e.g. Martin \"Chalky\" White). Mirrors the legacy webtrees behaviour for trees that store nicknames in the separate GEDCOM NICK field."
msgstr "将 GEDCOM NICK 字段的值用引号插入在名字与姓氏之间（例如 Martin \"Chalky\" White）。模拟旧版 webtrees 的行为，适用于在单独的 GEDCOM NICK 字段中保存昵称的家谱。"
